        <h1>Agence Lorem ipsum.</h1>
        <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Animi iusto saepe tenetur!
            Ab consequuntur dolores eaque facere in iste laboriosam officia quibusdam, recusandae ut. Ad explicabo modi nobis quis voluptate.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Les derniers bien</h2>
        <div class="row flex">
            {% for property in properties %}
                <div class="col-3">
                    <div class="card">
                        <div class="card-body">
